      "updated": 1776160868478,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Stage 1 — Data Preparation (pre-federation)",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Stage 1 — Data Preparation (pre-federation)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "H5fgFGxUuMFpkZozz94a0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8110961914062,
      "y": 171.31640625,
      "width": 769.999755859375,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBc",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 723114467,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 60968987,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776160868478,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cohort discovery happens offline during initial\ndiscussions about a new FLIP project, defining the\ntarget population and data requirements.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Cohort discovery happens offline during initial discussions about a new FLIP project, defining the target population and data requirements.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "u8RoXYnNo0c4szQ5g-xEF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -589.5111083984375,
      "y": 233.81640625,
      "width": 785.3997802734375,
      "height": 210,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBd",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 259221965,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 981373717,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776160868478,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Once approved by the Data Access Committee, Trust\ndata is ingested into the TRE through the TRE SOP —\nOMOP data is synced in batches (including\nanonymisation) and DICOMs are pushed per-project\nfrom PACS (including anonymisation and defacing\nwhere needed).",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Once approved by the Data Access Committee, Trust data is ingested into the TRE through the TRE SOP — OMOP data is synced in batches (including anonymisation) and DICOMs are pushed per-project from PACS (including anonymisation and defacing where needed).",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "WTMzG_2En-XYk1JamE7Cb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -512.5111083984375,
      "y": 586.31640625,
      "width": 631.3997802734375,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBe",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1663739267,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 548902075,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776160868478,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Stage 2 — Federated Learning / Evaluation",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Stage 2 — Federated Learning / Evaluation",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "_46kLSUQViHZN3mJjUVGc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8110961914062,
      "y": 658.81640625,
      "width": 769.999755859375,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBf",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 912173101,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 398813301,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776160868478,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FLIP users run cohort queries against the TRE OMOP\ndatabase to select the relevant subset of data.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FLIP users run cohort queries against the TRE OMOP database to select the relevant subset of data.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "KNFwnzFM_6abNF8IA5W8y",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -566.4111328125,
      "y": 738.81640625,
      "width": 739.1998291015625,
      "height": 70,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBg",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1650523427,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 1073431899,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776160868478,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "XNAT pulls the corresponding imaging data into a\ndedicated project where images can be enriched.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "XNAT pulls the corresponding imaging data into a dedicated project where images can be enriched.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0F_yBNV8sOtD1Uz68RV_w",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -581.8110961914062,
      "y": 801.31640625,
      "width": 769.999755859375,
      "height": 105,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bBh",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 773003917,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 1145737685,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776160868478,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "FLIP users submit AI model training/inference jobs\nthat use GPU resources. Only aggregated cohort\nstats and aggregated model weights leave the TRE.",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "FLIP users submit AI model training/inference jobs that use GPU resources. Only aggregated cohort stats and aggregated model weights leave the TRE.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
